OL,6,FFour people have been arrested in
OL,7,FNewport in connection with the supply
OL,8,Fof class A drugs.
OL,10,FGwent Police made the arrests on
OL,11,FThursday morning (20 February) in the
OL,12,FAlway and Bettws areas of the city.
OL,13,FDuring the arrests, officers recovered
OL,14,Fa quantity of cash and mobile phones,
OL,15,Falongside class A drugs.
OL,17,FA man and a woman, both aged 19, were
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of being
OL,19,Fconcerned in the supply of class A
OL,20,Fdrugs and possession with intent to
OL,21,Fsupply class A drugs.
