OL,6,FResponding to the arrests, PC Jack
OL,7,FPassmore, neighbourhood ward manager
OL,8,Ffor Alway, said: "Intelligence we
OL,9,Freceive from the public is paramount
OL,10,Fas we combat the production, sale and
OL,11,Fsupply of illegal drugs in the Newport
OL,12,Farea.
OL,14,F"We hope this morning's warrants show
OL,15,Fthat input from local residents really
OL,16,Fdoes make a difference, so please
OL,17,Fcontinue to report your concerns and
OL,18,Finformation to us."
