OL,6,FHe added: "Illegal drugs fill our
OL,7,Fcommunities with misery, suffering and
OL,8,Ffear and those involved prey upon the
OL,9,Fvulnerable in our society.
OL,11,F"If you have any concerns about
OL,12,Fillegal drugs in your area, let us
OL,13,Fknow by calling 101 or direct
OL,14,Fmessaging us on our Facebook or X
OL,15,Fpages, so that we can take action.
OL,17,F"Alternatively, you can call
OL,18,FCrimestoppers, anonymously, on 0800
OL,19,F555 111, with information or contact
OL,20,Fthem via their website."
